<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>Evesham Community Hospital  has a pay and display car park for visitors.The fee is 50p per hour and there are 202 spaces, 122 of which are for patients and visitors and 6 of these are reserved for disabled badge holders.</p>
